data.title: Place Explorer
data.text:
The Place Explorer tool helps you understand the core data underlying a place. It pulls together a set of charts on the demographics, education, economics, etc., of the place, placing them in context with comparisons to other places. You can also see how different places rank along different metrics like unemployment, crime and income.

You can dive into the charts for your favorite city, zipcode, county, state or country using the search box above.

Or, start exploring some well known places ...
